{"tid":180542,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好想自殺死左佢算數","createTime":"2017-03-31T03:50:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-08T12:23:03.000Z","uid":63555,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"57348a06c6cc79fdd397053388b53f7fb73e6fd6","tid":180542,"uid":63555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T03:50:49.000Z","msg":"人生為乜 生存好迷失。"},{"pid":"b7b75b3b2a6d4e64dbc8adc7b304c0e5bea805c1","tid":180542,"uid":72769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T03:52:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b205658fea509f2add7709c04a3bb0b5919c052","tid":180542,"uid":63555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T03:54:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔想一屍兩命 可以點算"},{"pid":"56bc66d5b6f5485e8c0d2de1a0ee42f71ed99c24","tid":180542,"uid":50658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T03:57:19.000Z","msg":"講嚟聽下"},{"pid":"045c19d8fad4da32f89d09dbb924c9f8c55e8fa2","tid":180542,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T03:58:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔想一屍兩命 可以點算</blockquote><br />\n合上眼 深呼吸<br />\n你知唔知自殺投唔到骷<br />\n只少要等到陽壽盡之前係人間一直抱住怨念徘徊<br />\n死左絕對唔係一了百了<br />\n有咩人有咩事 令你煩擾 咪離開囉有咩大不了<br />\n自己自己自己 重生存先係最重要既一件事<br />\n無人或者事值得你放棄<br />\n唔開心係度分享下 請勇敢面對生活"},{"pid":"fb23b0ba990f3560157b53708c91c5c263da06ed","tid":180542,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T03:59:57.000Z","msg":"樓豬我唔係想駁你<br />\n我想你諗下點解要強迫自己要有人生意義先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實你自己生活得開心就得啦<br />\n唔使夾硬搵目標"},{"pid":"2684a09d6eec42b8b1909f3fe3a284c26a5193b8","tid":180542,"uid":63555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T04:05:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓豬我唔係想駁你<br />\n我想你諗下點解要強迫自己要有人生意義先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實你自己生活得開心就得啦<br />\n唔使夾硬搵目標</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n依家就係生活得好唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e28deb7045c66835d9f77ad620c62235984e5f4e","tid":180542,"uid":63555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T04:06:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講嚟聽下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好後悔咁早結婚 咁早有小朋友"},{"pid":"d287c8f3a7c02638e42befbfbd2b8dba70f0043b","tid":180542,"uid":79199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T04:21:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓豬我唔係想駁你<br />\n我想你諗下點解要強迫自己要有人生意義先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實你自己生活得開心就得啦<br />\n唔使夾硬搵目標</blockquote><br />\nYes 一定要有人生意義架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我冇興趣同目標廢青一名,同班fd玩得開心又一日，根本唔駛理咩意義<br />\nBtw 我最唔鍾意人地開口埋口講自殺，你又知死左之後既世界係點？一定係輕鬆？如果都係要讀書返工點算先？ff 咁講如果死後好似宗教所講要受刑又會係輕鬆咩？<br />\n人生在世，不如諗下自己有咩想做先啦，去做自己喜歡既事，從中可能搵到意義都未定<br />\nBtw 不如樓主講下有咩煩惱？講出黎會舒服啲，連登巴絲可能幫到你呢，記住連登有愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"370bfe93e39a9217669d7cbeeca99c3be4053b7c","tid":180542,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T04:23:33.000Z","msg":"樓主似係產前抑鬱喎！"},{"pid":"7a65aa3b2b13245f32d876178a99294cf889f6f1","tid":180542,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T04:24:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓豬我唔係想駁你<br />\n我想你諗下點解要強迫自己要有人生意義先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實你自己生活得開心就得啦<br />\n唔使夾硬搵目標</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n依家就係生活得好唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咩原因令你唔開心先？<br />\n講出黎先解決到架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"703c728e93d3a2a66272fda7532f9763d3918681","tid":180542,"uid":73935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T04:27:46.000Z","msg":"產前抑鬱"},{"pid":"c63701549d5abb150e504a8520770d57380c6c7f","tid":180542,"uid":68846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T04:57:39.000Z","msg":"我都想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dd02bc57ccef3b99f187e31fdcbcfbe5d756e51","tid":180542,"uid":63555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T04:58:44.000Z","msg":"覺得自己做人好失敗 望住自己屋企人咁辛苦"},{"pid":"f10cac27b441fe8fe7c1da207ebb317102fe5a26","tid":180542,"uid":187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T07:22:51.000Z","msg":"個仔幾大"},{"pid":"1d23df3a4b85db75be96f424fcd79aee27d25c14","tid":180542,"uid":72769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T07:34:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>覺得自己做人好失敗 望住自己屋企人咁辛苦</blockquote><br />\n如果你宜家走左 你屋企人仲傷心 仲辛苦<br />\n為左肚入面嗰個唔好放棄自己<br />\n做仆街好易 有咩唔想理 放低唔理就行<br />\n但自己條路自己揀 肚入面嗰個無得揀<br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e281d408d407e1968c7c1b9fbe89f2a848a49e33","tid":180542,"uid":187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T07:40:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>覺得自己做人好失敗 望住自己屋企人咁辛苦</blockquote><br />\n如果你宜家走左 你屋企人仲傷心 仲辛苦<br />\n為左肚入面嗰個唔好放棄自己<br />\n做仆街好易 有咩唔想理 放低唔理就行<br />\n但自己條路自己揀 肚入面嗰個無得揀<br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n樓主話想做老豆<br />\n應該男人黎"},{"pid":"6796dd4c122876c678b79f7bf76ac9d01c311234","tid":180542,"uid":72769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T07:52:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>覺得自己做人好失敗 望住自己屋企人咁辛苦</blockquote><br />\n如果你宜家走左 你屋企人仲傷心 仲辛苦<br />\n為左肚入面嗰個唔好放棄自己<br />\n做仆街好易 有咩唔想理 放低唔理就行<br />\n但自己條路自己揀 肚入面嗰個無得揀<br />\n加油<img src=\